Package: cct
Version: 1.0.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: systemd
Recommends: xdg-utils
Maintainer: CCT Maintainers <maintainer@example.com>
Description: Claude Context Tracker - Native Ubuntu Application
 Track and manage context for your Claude Code projects.
 Never lose important details when conversations get compacted.
 .
 This native Ubuntu application includes:
  - Pre-built web dashboard (no npm setup required!)
  - Desktop launcher in Applications menu
  - CLI tool for quick context operations
  - Daemon for monitoring Claude Code conversations
  - PocketBase database backend (auto-starts as systemd service)
 .
 Simply install and launch from your Applications menu!
